WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.870
Lupan The 3RD

2
00:00:12.030 --> 00:00:16.950
Opening Theme "Lupan za Saado No Uta"
Lupan III Song "Vocals: Charlie Kosei.

3
00:00:26.830 --> 00:00:31.010
Original Story: Monkey Punch
Serialized in:Weekly Manga Action

